    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Among the twenty signs of the Nahua calendar, four of them (calli, tochtli, acatl and tecpatl) were also used to designate the name of the solar years of the xiuhpohualli (solar calendar of three hundred and sixty five days).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000320/GRI-FloCo</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000109721/GRI, FloCo terminology (2019-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Entre los veinte signos del calendario nahua, cuatro de ellos (calli, tochtli, acatl y tecpatl) se utilizaron también para designar el nombre de los años solares del xiuhpohualli (calendario solar de trescientos sesenta y cinco días).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000320/GRI-FloCo</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000109721/GRI, FloCo terminology (2019-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ica cempohualli tlaixnextilli tlen tonalpohuatl nahuatl, nahui tlen ni (calli, tochtli, acatl  huan tecpatl) motequihuihqueh para quimanextizceh itocan nopa xihuitl solares tlen xiuhpohualli (tonalpohualli solar tlen quipiya eyi ciento huan epohualli huan caxtolli tonatiuh).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000320/GRI-FloCo</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
